":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c8201376eb18f5a5805aded563a04cba707a434","tid":1512362,"uid":61974,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T08:45:45.000Z","msg":"唔講佢咩立場先<br />\n其實吉野家真係好難食<br />\n啲牛肉同汁勁咸勁多咪精又唔係特別平<br />\n點解香港人咁鍾情呢間野<br />\n就算佢係黃絲餐廳我都要諗諗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T09:22:22.000Z","msg":"好難食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n順便戒牛啦各位"},{"pid":"8d5f72e0fa5775896b8d0725197dcb051adc5362","tid":1512362,"uid":298759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T09:23:20.000Z","msg":"尋晚八點零，第一城間吉野八成空<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n薩莉亞爆人唔講，連隔離KFC都多人過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96731a08417a52de6a7a9e5b1591c7dc64b54452","tid":1512362,"uid":274722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T09:23:39.000Z","msg":"排完吉野家再去新城巿排喜茶，盡顯大灣區巿民核心價值"},{"pid":"4163cf45342932406fde73bc8bd31ffeede3aa85","tid":1512362,"uid":7849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T09:24:29.000Z","msg":"始終都有藍絲廢老蝗蟲食，但相比起以前已經少左好多人。<br />\n利申：一次都冇再食過"},{"pid":"16ea9f2d558150b416b9c8701ad0ea53475d8b9c","tid":1512362,"uid":226126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T12:11:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fff99121741837ce03c134bfd36fa1734e2acb5e","tid":1512362,"uid":282490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf810227ea512c073da4f7ac0f8d9204b4deea83","tid":1512362,"uid":44074,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T07:16:18.000Z","msg":"比啲骨氣啦香港人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T12:15:21.000Z","msg":"Give them alternatives <br />\n<br />\n可否叫加藤屋喺沙田開分店"},{"pid":"e5996d69a21d71a31a895939bffa10b1bf1508c4","tid":1512362,"uid":272652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T12:17:00.000Z","msg":"真係咁好食咩？又唔係平"},{"pid":"92b42b7e803b31e04d0f3e2da16532f02f4d43ca","tid":1512362,"uid":1197